quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  18,60,"Ndipo pamenepo Mose adamuuza mnyamata wake kuti, “Ine ndidzapitirirabe kuyenda mpaka pamene ndidzafika pamalo pamene nyanja ziwiri zikumana kapena ndidzapitirira kuyenda zaka ndi zaka.”"
  18,61,"Koma pamene iwo adafika pamalo pamene nyanja ziwiri zidakumana, iwo adaiwala nsomba yawo ndipo iyo idatenga njira yake yodutsa kupita m’madzi"
  18,62,"Ndipo iwo atapitiriza ulendo wawo, Mose adati kwa mnyamata wake, “Bweretsa chakudya chathu. Ndithudi tapeza, mu ulendo wathu, zotopetsa.”"
  18,63,"Iye adati, “Kodi iwe siudaone pathanthwe pamene tidapuma paja, kuti ine ndidaiwala nsomba ndipo palibe china chimene chidandiiwalitsa kuti ndiikumbukire koma Satana yemwe adandiiwalitsa. Ndipo iyo idalowa m’madzi mozizwitsa.”"
  18,64,"Mose adati, “Pamenepo ndi pamene timafuna.” Iwo adabwerera kulondola kumene adachokera"
  18,65,Ndipo iwo adam’peza mmodzi wa akapolo wathu amene tidamupatsa chifundo chochokera kwa Ife ndiponso tidamuphunzitsa nzeru zochokera kwa Ife
  18,66,"Mose adati kwa iye, “Kodi ndingakutsateni kuti mwina mundiphunzitse zabwino zina za zimene mudaphunzitsidwa?”"
  18,67,"Iye adati, “Ndithudi! Iwe siudzatha kupirira ndi ine.”"
  18,68,Kodi iwe ungapirire bwanji pa zinthu zimene suli kuzidziwa
  18,69,"Mose adati, “Ngati Mulungu afuna, udzandipeza ine ndili wopirira ndipo ine sindidzakunyoza iwe ayi.”"
  18,70,"Iye adati, “Ngati iwe unganditsatire, usandifunse china chilichonse chimene ungawone mpaka pamene ine nditakuuza za chinthucho.”"